{"tid":738271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際聯繫】Vox下週三開始播片介紹香港","createTime":"2018-07-11T11:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T05:50:08.000Z","uid":138409,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3170f1dafd4dc89f64c57b61aea1bb62a66d02","tid":738271,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxpQKzUNQdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSxpQKzUNQdA&d=DMF7AYdI%2B%2FHnh5No5QpxQXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f8129a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxpQKzUNQdA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/194530_02c33e49912b38458c7e0c774e3748de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F194530_02c33e49912b38458c7e0c774e3748de.png&h=0fa2da9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毛孟靜：&ldquo;Hong Kong will be gobbled up&rdquo; (「香港將被吞噬」)<br />\n</span><br />\n7月18日開始，每逢星期三，Vox Border向世界展示香港的不同面貌<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong sits on one of the world&rsquo;s most peculiar borders. It&rsquo;s a part of China but it&rsquo;s also very much an independent entity. Every Wednesday for five weeks, Vox&rsquo;s Johnny Harris goes behind the scenes in Hong Kong, talking to the locals and showcasing some of the interesting culture that emerged in this nexus between East and West.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/194442_882ee78430d64de091f245bf81a6414c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F194442_882ee78430d64de091f245bf81a6414c.png&h=9d6c37a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n雖然Vox係左膠媒體之餘又反侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有外媒報導下增加香港國際曝光率都無錯"},{"pid":"66d0ad437e61a0f9b9f2c950b164d931aaa6081a","tid":738271,"uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/194939_b49b69359e88e93560e2691718c3f89d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F194939_b49b69359e88e93560e2691718c3f89d.png&h=1ac02a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Oh, and not to be ignored: the big border up north that feels an awful lot like an international border <span style=\"color: red;\">between two countries</span>&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4131153c3ef253ba79ccbae05545e1484e7716dd","tid":738271,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/195218_62279252319cb558409221366daa69a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F195218_62279252319cb558409221366daa69a2.png&h=e902a636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/195221_519449f8a73bdf72d96e55381aa3a799.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F195221_519449f8a73bdf72d96e55381aa3a799.png&h=ffd8cddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;Everything from why hundreds of thousands of Hong Kongers are living in houses the size of coffins&quot;</span>"},{"pid":"3b8b4a7acc0413a3b5990e26435d42febe19e33b","tid":738271,"uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/195432_89ad5d53dcfbecf6bde40764345bc62a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F195432_89ad5d53dcfbecf6bde4076